text: Return from Hell () is a 1983 Romanian drama movie directed by Nicolae Mărgineanu and starring Constantin Brînzea, Maria Ploae, Remus Margineanu, Ana Ciontea, Ion Sasaran, Vasile Nitulescu. It was distributed by Româniafilm. == Other websites == * Category:1983 drama movies Category:Romanian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Nicolae Mărgineanu
